snippet.title: Gus Goes to Cybertown (HD, Full Songs, Full Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Gus Goes to Cybertown is a children's game from 1993. You need an old computer (Windows ME, 98 or older) or a VM to run it. 

I uploaded this before but people said they wanted the full songs so here's a higher quality version with full songs and more of the game played through.
